        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28410034/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28410034/" class="">第4页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/47614548/" class=" " title="鲁为鱼">鲁为鱼</a>
                (直面庸常)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="28410034">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">哈氏立论起点：人类是如何从早期原始社会休戚与共的小部落，发展成广土众民、和睦相处并形成巨大而复杂交往关系的巨型社会的呢？</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-09-03 20:33</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">2人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>哈氏立论起点：人类是如何从早期原始社会休戚与共的小部落，发展成广土众民、和睦相处并形成巨大而复杂交往关系的巨型社会的呢？</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







